# IVSCS — Intelligent Vehicle Safety & Control System

An interactive browser dashboard simulating the four layers of the IVSCS:

| Layer | Description |
|-------|-------------|
| **01 — Sensing** | Real-time wheel grip, vibration, ultrasonic distance, camera object detection |
| **02 — AI Processing** | Radar view, collision-risk ring, AI decision log |
| **03 — Action** | ECU torque control, smart braking, anti-skid, safety balloon deployment |
| **04 — Workflow** | 5-step logic flow highlighted in real time |

## Getting Started

Open `index.html` directly in any modern browser — no build step required.

## File Structure

```
IVSCS/
├── index.html          Main HTML shell & layout
├── css/
│   └── style.css       All styles, variables, animations
└── js/
    ├── state.js        Central vehicle state object
    ├── radar.js        Canvas radar renderer
    ├── ui.js           DOM update functions & AI log
    ├── scenarios.js    Four simulation scenarios
    └── main.js         Boot, clock, noise, animation loop
```

## Scenarios

| Button | What happens |
|--------|-------------|
| **Normal** | Baseline cruise with gentle sensor noise |
| **Slippery** | Icy road — anti-skid + ECU torque reduction engage |
| **Object** | Pedestrian detected — emergency brake → safe stop |
| **Rear Hit** | Rear collision imminent — safety balloon deploys |




